  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>General</Type>
    <Text>The outdoor swimming pool is located on the same floor as the lobby, behind the reception area. This property is recommended for budget travellers who would like to stay in a hotel near the airport.  (06/09SW)</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>SurroundingArea</Type>
    <Text>Located on Pattanakarn Road, this property offers easy access to Secon Square and Seri Centre Shopping Mall and the new Suvarnabhumi airport, which is 20 minutes away by car.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>RoomTypes</Type>
    <Text>All guest rooms are large size, a master bedroom and living area. Rooms provide good panoramic views of the surrounding area. Room decoration is simple. Some have hardwood floors and others are carpeted. Bathrooms are shower only. Each floor has only 8 rooms, providing privacy for guests.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>PropertyInformation</Type>
    <Text>The light green high-rise building is made of concrete and glass.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>DiningFacilities</Type>
    <Text>There is a coffee shop next to lobby offering all-day dining and a menu of international cuisines.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>Short</Type>
    <Text>The medium-sized lobby provides moderns sofa and rattan seats. An Internet corner is also available to guests. There is a Lobby Lounge next to the lobby.</Text>
  </Description>
